{"tid":2233953,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"依架啲私家醫生收費都幾貴","createTime":"2020-10-07T13:37:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-08T10:34:47.000Z","uid":37238,"like":35,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"c9af472b8643c948cf23943aa1b4ee6576f17e57","tid":2233953,"uid":37238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T13:37:07.000Z","msg":"之前一直用開醫療卡睇醫生 所以比較少留意診金啲問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n話說前排轉咗新公司 冇晒之前啲醫療福利<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n早幾日個肚痾到仆街 落咗樓下好多年冇去間診所掛號夜診 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n點知睇完 埋單計數普通診金500 連埋特效藥夾埋700蚊 我當堂睇到打個突<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n俾錢嗰明明五六年前 間嘢都係收緊250左右 點解過咗一排會貴咗咁撚多<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n到底係依架啲診金真係咁撚貴 定係樓豬俾人搵笨？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />樓豬之前太離地 依架睇醫生真係好撚貴<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />樓豬on9 咁都可以俾醫生搵笨"},{"pid":"bef612d6888fe1736226d4db7d0f296f9b4718d9","tid":2233953,"uid":61763,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T13:38:06.000Z","msg":"中環專科一千起跳未計藥"},{"pid":"468d7ad7303636e2416a39620c9265d744ea4c2c","tid":2233953,"uid":37238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bef612d6888fe1736226d4db7d0f296f9b4718d9","tid":2233953,"uid":61763,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T13:38:06.000Z","msg":"中環專科一千起跳未計藥"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T13:42:13.000Z","msg":"專科嘅話我都叫理解 但係講緊落診所睇普通科 仲要唔係啲咩高貴地段<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a408780fed356f9c502ee9f7a30bf1747738c1da","tid":2233953,"uid":61763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"468d7ad7303636e2416a39620c9265d744ea4c2c","tid":2233953,"uid":37238,"like":0,"dislike